<app-fail-modal
  *ngIf="modalService.showPopup && modalService.type == 0"
></app-fail-modal>
<app-loading-modal
  *ngIf="modalService.showPopup && modalService.type == 2"
></app-loading-modal>
<app-success-modal
  *ngIf="modalService.showPopup && modalService.type == 1"
></app-success-modal>
<app-warning-modal
  *ngIf="modalService.showPopup && modalService.type == 3"
></app-warning-modal>
<router-outlet></router-outlet>
import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http';
import { Component } from '@angular/core';
import { ModalService } from './services/modal.service';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-root',
  templateUrl: './app.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./app.component.css']
})
export class AppComponent {

  constructor(http: HttpClient, public modalService: ModalService) {
    
  }

  title = 'CarManagementClient';
}
